{
  "stem": "22652.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she made a living by cleaning wealthy people's homes and sewing and bringing home sometimes the ironing and the sewing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember she sewed buttons on soldiers' uniforms and just any sewing that needed to be done.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I was always aware that I was different, you know, because my parents spoke Yiddish at home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a thick foreign accent when they spoke French.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they sometimes spoke incorrectly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as a child, I had that feeling of embarrassment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were poor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, everyone in our neighborhood was poor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We all saw each other on the bread line over in City Hall to be outfitted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So what was your question?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How did you feel different?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or, did you feel different being Jewish?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that, when my father was arrested as a Jew, and I think prior to that-- I can't pinpoint the date.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From the moment that my mother sewed [SOBBING] the Jewish star, the Jewish yellow star on our clothing, the two of us and all our Jewish friend had to go out to wear that yellow star, with the word [NON-ENGLISH], Jew, I think from that moment on, my being part of French civilization kind of set me apart.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I-- I used to walk with my head down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Although, I must say that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because our Jewish-- non-Jewish friends and neighbors were always very kind to us [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and teachers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was an atheist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, he was militant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother did not discuss religion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have a brother who is still living in Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He is a very religious Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my aunt from America was-- she was semi-religious.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
